title: No Hope v1.0
description:
No Hope is a fast-paced survival top down shooter, where your goal is to fight against the incoming enemies, collect materials and defend the safe house.

Enjoy a fun pick-up-and-play style game with impressive hand-painted graphics and glorious explosions!

Features
- 6 Different weapons
- 8 Different perks
- 20 Waves of run-and-gun action
- 30 Achievements
- Safe house improvements
